application/x-www-form-urlencoded
提交方式

参数需要使用 http_build_query();处理  其对应的反函数是  parse_str();



ase cbc模式 补全加密
function ase_cbc($data, $secret) {
        $data = json_encode($data);
        $encrypted = openssl_encrypt($data, 'AES-128-CBC', $secret, 1, $secret);
        return base64_encode($encrypted);
    }   

解密
    function ase_cbc_de($data, $secret) {
        $data = base64_decode($data);
        $decrypted = openssl_decrypt($data, 'AES-128-CBC', $secret, 1, $secret);
        return json_decode($decrypted, 1); 
    }   



